author: Joshua
title: Joshua
text:
Chinese parts is great way to get my parts for my motorbike they all came fast and brilliant also ringing them was having great customer service but do need to know more about the items there selling so can help us a bit more on say what's wrong with the item.
Also needs to be full tracked couldn't track my items due to your delivery.
But all the end I be using this site straight for all my parts
